{"tid":211533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係西九唔見咗卡套入面有五張卡 求集氣","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T08:09:49.000Z","uid":17825,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8b067acc76f5f354df27c51a37462e35081d6c","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"小妹借男朋友個acc嚟po 希望連登有愛大家集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的 大概九點幾個陣去咗西九打算食薩莉亞 趁要等位就打算行七樓蘋果商場點知收曬就落返去等位 咁食完個陣已經係十點幾所以嗱嗱聲係三樓去完廁所就走 點知走咗之後等緊馬路個陣打算摷定八達通搭車個陣就發現平時攝係褲袋嘅卡套唔見咗 冇得返去搵因爲西九已經就删門連電梯都停埋同埋已經比老母屌遲返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有巴絲聽日會去西九既可唔可以幫手留意吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個卡套係同男朋友一人一個 上個星期先送比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入面攝曬我同佢一齊睇既戲飛尾 全部跌咗就冇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有遵理同學校學生證八達通海洋公園pass同starbucks卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 八達通啲錢我可以唔要但執到可唔可以比返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入面張八達通同遵理學生證用咗好多年好感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有人咁好彩執到可唔可以留低tg比我聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上卡套個樣同starbucks卡個款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該曬大家 我知自己唔小心同大意 希望大家可以屌細力啲之餘可以搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/22/003342_c85d9024400af013431156cfdad5700c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F22%2F003342_c85d9024400af013431156cfdad5700c.jpg&h=fa7c352a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Qh9nDn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Qh9nDn.jpg&h=706a5af6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1081163837b3a5cb829e5dce2e8f81dfc87a8ef7","tid":211533,"uid":84951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3201b5983de8033971b2aac874a130251d5364e","tid":211533,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"戲飛尾上既字會隨時間消失，同男女之間既感情一樣，留黎都無意思<br />\n學生證可以換，八達通可以換，沒甚麼好留戀，你幼稚園張學生證仲有無拎出黎睇？無既話你只係自以爲張學生證對自己好重要，其實當有新代替品後連一眼都唔會望"},{"pid":"13c6714f89d0aaf4ae4c423f2b4bb58146e25bd9","tid":211533,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦臭雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af85e51b37f60f011237e31d6f0b879e2d2c45f","tid":211533,"uid":89743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:53:09.000Z","msg":"西九跌咁多窮撚一定冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n快啲開apps打電話cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8d274d5348a26f5e3d4cce45e99d38444a8f51","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西九跌咁多窮撚一定冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n快啲開apps打電話cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCut咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我最唔捨得係啲戲飛尾 同男朋友每一場睇既戲飛尾都有keep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係呢幾張冇擺返屋企一直攝係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一諗起就想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5da81dd88f132ee97059d50e0f7b88ff71b23e2","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戲飛尾上既字會隨時間消失，同男女之間既感情一樣，留黎都無意思<br />\n學生證可以換，八達通可以換，沒甚麼好留戀，你幼稚園張學生證仲有無拎出黎睇？無既話你只係自以爲張學生證對自己好重要，其實當有新代替品後連一眼都唔會望</blockquote><br />\n其實係仲有好多補領好煩好多野搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d42391c3d30ef6f1b76be4c50d8f58f57af0a4","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"各位未瞓嘅巴絲可唔可以幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c72d4ad168b481a7fb7b0a7e25ba039e0308db3","tid":211533,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"隨時被偷"},{"pid":"c8f05ef61ef41069d2aebe17865d5878865360a0","tid":211533,"uid":102056,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef316ff230544fab0ff4eaa4041dba87cc67a787","tid":211533,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22c9b1fefa680186d1c3a127ca8da3993a6c1eab","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨時被偷</blockquote><br />\n已經過咗一日仲係乜消息都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95f86458bdd9279b9e7bc24ff605512d443f640","tid":211533,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友有撚用咩、快d去做ptgf、大把男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乖女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535e6c4ff4802a307f1174962f76751dde417015","tid":211533,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci